11000 ! 11000 - Convert numeric strings to number
11010 STR_TO_NUM:
11020 _X$="INV_AMT",_X=INV_AMT.CTL,INV_AMT=NUM(INV_AMT$,ERR=NON_NUMERIC)
11030 _X$="NET_SALE",_X=NET_SALE.CTL,NET_SALE=NUM(NET_SALE$,ERR=NON_NUMERIC)
